    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "function extractText(nodeName) {\n  try {\n    const item = $(nodeName).first();\n    if (!item || !item.json) return '(no data returned)';\n    const raw = item.json;\n    let payload = raw;\n    if (raw.content && Array.isArray(raw.content) && raw.content[0]) {\n      payload = raw.content[0].text !== undefined ? raw.content[0].text : raw.content[0];\n    } else if (Array.isArray(raw) && raw[0]) {\n      payload = raw[0].text !== undefined ? raw[0].text : raw[0];\n    }\n    if (typeof payload === 'string') {\n      const trimmed = payload.trim();\n      if (trimmed.startsWith('{') || trimmed.startsWith('[')) {\n        try { return JSON.stringify(JSON.parse(trimmed), null, 2); } catch(e) { return payload; }\n      }\n      return payload;\n    }\n    return JSON.stringify(payload, null, 2);\n  } catch(e) {\n    return `(extraction error: ${e.message})`;\n  }\n}\n\nconst resolved = $('Resolve IDs').first().json;\nconst target = $('Set Target').first().json;\nreturn [{ json: {\n  ...resolved,\n  ...target,\n  accountStatus: extractText('Get Account Status'),\n  recentActivity: extractText('Get Recent Account Activity'),\n  situationSearch: extractText('Situation Search'),\n  salesAiAnswer: extractText('Ask SalesAI: Next Action'),\n} }];"
      },
      "id": "9d9eb5fd-ef83-49ca-a150-3bac6e19a01f",
      "name": "Merge MCP Results",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1104,
        1984
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const j = $json;\nconst prompt = `You are an AI revenue orchestration agent. A signal fired on a deal and you must propose two specific, approval-gated actions.\n\nSignal: ${j.signal_type}\nDeal: ${j.opportunity_name} | Account: ${j.account_name}\nOwner: ${j.opportunity_owner}\n\n## Account Status\n${j.accountStatus}\n\n## Recent Activity\n${j.recentActivity}\n\n## Comparable Deals (Situation Search)\n${j.situationSearch}\n\n## SalesAI Analysis\n${j.salesAiAnswer}\n\nPropose exactly two actions. Output STRICT JSON only — no markdown, no code fences, no preamble:\n\n{\n  \"summary\": \"2-sentence summary of why these actions are being proposed\",\n  \"crm_update\": {\n    \"field\": \"NextStep__c\",\n    \"value\": \"Proposed next step (under 200 chars)\",\n    \"rationale\": \"1-2 sentence rationale based on activity evidence\"\n  },\n  \"slack_message\": {\n    \"message\": \"Proposed Slack DM to deal owner — direct, specific, references comparable situation, under 200 words\",\n    \"rationale\": \"1-2 sentence rationale based on Situation Search\"\n  }\n}\n\nReturn ONLY the JSON object. No code fences. No explanation.`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...j, prompt } }];"
      },
